(67,	'Cooperate Social Responsibility',	'<p>As a caring organization the BPS engages in social responsibility activities to give back to the community it serves. Some of such activities are as follows:</p>\r\n      \r\n      <h3>2007</h3>\r\n      \r\n      <ul class=\"listing\">\r\n      <li>Commissioner&rsquo;s donation of P10,000.00 to UCCSA Church,  Molepolole Branch.</li>\r\n      <li>Commissioner donation of P10,000.00 to Bathusi  Support Group, Marobela</li>\r\n      <li>Raising of P112,000.00 to medical expenses of  Sergeant Moseki&rsquo;s ailing child</li>\r\n      <li>Kutlwano   Police Station donation of groceries and P1800.00 to a home based care  colleague</li>\r\n      <li>SIS Selibi Phikwe P5,000.00 donation to  Masiela Trust Fund</li>\r\n      <li>Naledi Police donation of two blankets and  toiletry to a needy person in Old Naledi</li>\r\n      <li>SIS Kanye donation of six tables, six table  cloths, groceries and P400 to Kanye Home Based Care.</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n      \r\n      <h3>2008</h3>\r\n		\r\n      <ul class=\"listing\">\r\n      <li>BPS donated shelter, clothing and household equipment to the tune of P106,000.00 to disadvantaged members of the community</li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n		\r\n        <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n        <div class=\"well\">\r\n        <h4 class=\"text-center\">For more information on Cooperate Social Responsibility contact 3914941</h4>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n\r\n',	'Cooperate-Social-Responsibility',	'mcms',	'Main Pages',	'2017-11-14',	'',	'',	'',	'bps-content.php?cid=67',	NULL,	'',	'18:45:53',	0,	NULL,	'',	''),
