(63,	'Victims and Witness Support',	'<ul class=\\\"listing\\\">\r\n  <li>Victims - There are supported by  offering them counselling and   protection where there is clear evidence that  he/she is under threat.</li>\r\n  <li>Witnesses - There are supported  by offering them protection   where there is clear evidence that he/she is under  threat. Moreover, in   cases where they have to travel long distance and in cases  where they   will need food, they are provided with transport, accommodation and    food.</li>\r\n</ul>',	'Victims and Witness Support',	'mcms',	'29',	'2017-11-14',	NULL,	'Active',	NULL,	'bps-content.php?cid=63',	NULL,	NULL,	'18:41:37',	0,	NULL,	'',	''),
(64,	'Violent and Intrusive Crime',	'<p>In cases of Armed Robberies, Robberies and their attempts  people are   attacked on the streets especially in dark areas. Occasionally    business community is targeted and robbed large sum of money after being    threatened with dangerous weapons.</p>\r\n<p>People are advised to avoid dark areas and also to avoid  going   un-accompanied during the night. The business community is advised to    always secure their premises by hiring reputable security services and    installing CCTV.</p>        \r\n     ',	'Violent and Intrusive Crime',	'mcms',	'29',	'2017-11-14',	NULL,	'Active',	NULL,	'bps-content.php?cid=64',	NULL,	NULL,	'18:43:11',	0,	NULL,	'',	''),
