(215,	'Job Opportunities',	'<h3>\r\n	VACANCY: PRINCIPAL MEDICAL OFFICER&ndash;D2(1 Post)</h3>\r\n<h4>\r\n	VACANCY CIRCULAR NO.4 OF 2015</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n	Forensic Pathology is a Unit under the Forensic Science Services Branch of the Botswana Police Service. It is responsible for medicolegal investigation of deceased persons within the jurisdiction of Botswana and Botswana citizens who die outside the country.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Applicants are invited from suitably qualified candidates for the above post at the Botswana Police Service. Preference shall be given to locals. The position is tenable in the Gaborone.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>BPS Strategic Element</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Medical Degree, Doctor of Medicine (M.D)or Bachelor Medicine and Bachelor of Surgery(MBBS).</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>SALARY:</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	D2 (P231 708 &ndash; P255,828)</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>LEAVE:</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	30 working days per annum</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>BENEFITS:</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	(i) Optional contributory Medical Aid Scheme (Government Pays 50% and employee 50%)</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	(ii) Compulsory Contributory Pension Scheme for permanent and personable staff (Government pays 15% employee pays 5%)</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	(iii) and other related Allowances and Benefits.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>EXPERIENCE:</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Minimum of three (3) years experience at Senior Medical Officer position or six (6) years experience as a Medical Officer.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Knowledge in Post-mortem examinations will be an added advantage.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>MAIN PURPOSE OF THE JOB:</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	To perform medico legal post mortem cases (Road Traffic Accidents, Suicides, traumatic deaths etc.) and give expert evidence in court of law and other relevant stakeholders.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>Applications should be addressed to: </strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Commissioner of Police<br />\r\n	Private Bag 0012<br />\r\n	Gaborone, Botswana</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Or Hand Deliver to:<br />\r\n	Records Management Unit<br />\r\n	Botswana Police Headquarters, Government Enclave<br />\r\n	Gaborone</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>CLOSING DATE:</strong> 31/01/2018</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n',	'Job Opportunities',	'mcms',	'136',	'2018-01-30',	NULL,	'Active',	NULL,	'bps-content.php?cid=215',	NULL,	NULL,	'17:00:40',	136,	NULL,	'',	''),
