(188,	'Telecoms and Transport Branch(TTB)',	'<p>TTB is a branch established to ensure availability of Transport and Information Communication Technology (ICT) services to members of the Botswana Police Services. The Branch supports the Botswana Police Service with technologies that are intended to enable the Service to carry out its mandate and achieve its corporate vision.</p> \r\n<h3>The Branch has five main units as follows:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>TTB Headquarters</li>\r\n<li>Transport Unit</li>\r\n<li>Telecommunications Branch South</li>\r\n<li>Telecommunications Branch North </li>\r\n<li>Information Technology Unit </li>\r\n</ul>',	'Telecoms and Transport Branch(TTB)',	'mcms',	'182',	'2011-02-04',	NULL,	'Active',	NULL,	'bps-content.php?cid=188',	NULL,	NULL,	'14:32:01',	0,	0,	NULL,	NULL),
