(552,	'Victims and Witness Support ',	'<ul class=\\\"listing\\\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		Victims - There are supported by offering them counselling and protection where there is clear evidence that he/she is under threat.</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Witnesses - There are supported by offering them protection where there is clear evidence that he/she is under threat. Moreover, in cases where they have to travel long distance and in cases where they will need food, they are provided with transport, accommodation and food.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',	'Victims and Witness Support ',	'mcms',	'544',	'2017-11-13',	'',	'Active',	'',	'bps-content.php?cid=552',	NULL,	'',	'19:15:15',	0,	NULL,	'',	''),
(553,	'Violent and Intrusive Crime ',	'<p>\r\n	In cases of Armed Robberies, Robberies and their attempts people are attacked on the streets especially in dark areas. Occasionally business community is targeted and robbed large sum of money after being threatened with dangerous weapons.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	People are advised to avoid dark areas and also to avoid going un-accompanied during the night. The business community is advised to always secure their premises by hiring reputable security services and installing CCTV.</p>\r\n',	'Violent and Intrusive Crime ',	'mcms',	'544',	'2017-11-13',	'',	'Active',	'',	'bps-content.php?cid=553',	NULL,	'',	'19:16:26',	0,	NULL,	'',	''),
