(576,	'Request for Police Escort',	'\r\n\r\n<p>The escort is provided to;</p>\r\n<ul class=\\\"listing\\\">\r\n<li>\r\n		The branch provides escorts for members of the public where it is suspected that the community might be at risk of attack from criminals.</li>\r\n	<li>Payment of large amounts of money</li>\r\n    <li>Cash in transit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',	'Request for Police Escort',	'mcms',	'387',	'2017-11-14',	NULL,	'Active',	NULL,	'bps-content.php?cid=576',	NULL,	NULL,	'14:58:48',	387,	NULL,	'',	''),
(577,	'Request for Police Escort',	'<p>Botswana Police Service provides escort where it is suspected that there is a risk of attack from criminals. The escort may be requested from the nearest Police Station and is subject to approval.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The escort is provided to;</strong></p>\r\n<ul class=\\\"listing\\\">\r\n	<li>Payment of large amounts of money</li>\r\n    <li>Cash in transit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',	'Request for Police Escort',	'mcms',	'387',	'2017-11-14',	NULL,	'',	NULL,	'bps-content.php?cid=577',	NULL,	NULL,	'14:59:56',	387,	NULL,	'',	''),
(578,	'Request for Police Protection',	'<p>Botswana Police Service in its mandate articulated that the service shall be employed in and throughout Botswana to protect life and property, prevent and detect crime, repress internal disturbances, maintain security and public tranquility. Dully enforce all written laws with which it is charged and generally maintain peace. The Police provide an over dimensional escort service for commercial businesses where the transit of vehicles, animals, goods or equipment may affect road safety or disrupt the flow of traffic.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\\\"listing\\\">\r\n	<li>Political rallies</li>\r\n    <li>Demonstrations/petitions</li>\r\n    <li>Sponsored walk</li>\r\n    <li>Sporting activities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Prior arrangement with relevant authorities should always be made so that deployment can be arranged well on time before the commencement of the event.</p>\r\n',	'',	'mcms',	'152',	'2017-11-14',	NULL,	'Active',	NULL,	'bps-content.php?cid=578',	NULL,	NULL,	'15:18:04',	0,	NULL,	'',	''),
